Friendly reminder:

One can short a coin without hating it with every fibre of ones being.

One can long a coin without believing it will eradicate global hunger and poverty.

In common parlance, this phenomenon is known as trading. 

"Marry people, not coins"
- Bruce Lee https://t.co/0YWRpYCaI5

Best traders I know that became extremely successful have never gotten emotionally attached to altcoins.

Many ‘traders’ I know that blew their accounts fell in love with alts and held them to zero.
